#Forward all ssh and http connection requests from the internet to local system 192.168.1.5
#ACTION         SOURCE  DEST            PROTO   DEST    SOURCE  ORIGINAL
#                                       PORT    PORT(S) DEST
SECTION NEW

Invalid(DROP)   net     all             tcp
Invalid(DROP)   loc     all             tcp
SSH(ACCEPT)     net     $FW
SSH(ACCEPT)     loc     $FW
Ping(ACCEPT)    loc     $FW
Ping(ACCEPT)    net     $FW
HTTP(ACCEPT)    net     $FW
HTTP(ACCEPT)    loc     $FW
ACCEPT          loc     $FW             tcp 8080
ACCEPT          net     $FW             tcp 8080
ACCEPT          $FW     net
ACCEPT          $FW     loc
DNS(ACCEPT)     loc     $FW
DNS(ACCEPT)     net     $FW
